<div type="abstract"><head>Rat Johann III. von Hohenzollern, Burggraf von Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet im Namen von Paul Klieber, Bürger zu Nürnberg, wegen dessen Armleute in Allersdorf gemäß altem Herkommen von der Erhebung einer Steuer abzusehen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_131" id="65r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_131_r4l23"><expan>Burggr<ex>af</ex></expan> <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_131_r4l25"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / vns hat fürgelegt 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Hans </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_131_r4l24">Pauls </ab></add> klyeber <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> / vvie daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r4l26">man ~ ſein Armleute cʒu Alerſtorff 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒ </del> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vvegen cʒu beſtewren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r4l27">main / die doch vormals niht geſtewret <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Bit<ex>en</ex></expan> etc / daʒ Jr von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r4l28"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mit den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ſchicken vnd beſtellen wöllet / daʒ man <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r4l29"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Armleute <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laſſe / Als ſie von alter <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_131_r4l30">Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Bonifac<ex>ij</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_131" id="65r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Burggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt <add>Pauls</add> Klyeber,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, wie daz man sein armleute czu Alerstorff von
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wegen czu bestewren main, die doch
                        vormals niht gestewret <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                            <expan>Bit<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., daz ir von
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mit den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> schicken
                        und bestellen wöllet, daz man <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> armleute <expan>bleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        lasse, als sie von alter <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Bonifac<ex>ii</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
